---
const personalImageAlt = "Albert Llargués";
---

<article class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto perspective">
  <div id="card" class="relative w-full h-96 transition-transform duration-700 transform-style-preserve-3d cursor-pointer" onclick="this.classList.toggle('is-flipped')">
    
    <!-- Front -->
    <div class="absolute w-full h-full backface-hidden bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl shadow-lg flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4">
      <img
        src="/projects/foto-aboutme.jpg"
        alt={personalImageAlt}
        class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full mb-4 ring-2 ring-yellow-400 object-cover"
      />
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-2">👨‍💻 More about me</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400">Tap to flip</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Back -->
    <div class="absolute w-full h-full backface-hidden rotate-y-180 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 overflow-auto">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white mb-2">Hi! 👋</h3>
      <p class="text-md text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">
        I'm Albert from Spain, <strong>Barcelona</strong>, recently moved to Trondheim. After 10 years in the transports sector, I started learning to code by myself and taking courses to pursue my dream of becoming a programmer.
      </p>
      
      <p class="text-md text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">I studied:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-md text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li>🎓 Multiplatform App Development – Barcelona</li>
        <li>🎓 Back-End Development – Noroff (Norway)</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-md text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-2">
        I love crafting from scratch, solving problems, and working hard to achieve my goals. I gained experience by trying, testing, and creating diverse projects in different languages—some as final projects in my courses and others on my own.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>

<style>
  .perspective {
    perspective: 1000px;
  }

  #card {
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
  }

  .backface-hidden {
    backface-visibility: hidden;
  }

  .rotate-y-180 {
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
  }

  #card.is-flipped {
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
  }
</style>
